headline: Assessing Amphenol (APH) Valuation After Nvidia AI Chip Launch Earnings Expectations And Dividend Focus
summary: Amphenol (APH) is back in focus after Nvidia announced its Rubin AI chip platform at CES 2026, which analysts suggest could require denser use of connectors and support demand for Amphenol products. See our latest analysis for Amphenol. The Rubin news lands on top of an already strong run for Amphenol, with a 12.39% 90 day share price return and a very large 5 year total shareholder return of 338.87%.
